Dialogue.text: Good morning, Sector 7! Today is the 8th day of Jeha. In just three days, a very lucky podtown is going to behold the glory that is Overlord Aso.

Dialogue600.text: In other news, the CX-6 virus has started spreading in Sector 7. Officials say that widespread helmet usage can dramatically cut down on infection.

Dialogue609.text: Officials are also lame and canceled the Lady GooGoo concert, so what do they know?
